(ca bong kho tieu)

season fish with fish sauce, sugar, sliced thai chilis, sliced garlic, green onion on a plate

thin layer of broken rock sugar in oil. 

once sugar becomes brown, put fish and marinade liquids into pot. 

layer of fish 1-2 deep, water should go about halfway up should not need to add more

braise on stove low heat for a good bit, uncovered if need to reduce and covered otherwise.